OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,FThe family of a 33-year-old woman who
OL,7,Fdied after her car was struck by a
OL,8,Ftrain at a level crossing have paid
OL,9,Ftribute to the "devoted mum" who "had
OL,10,Fthe biggest heart".
OL,12,FKerry Coombes, was killed at the level
OL,13,Fcrossing, on Station Road, in Hoghton,
OL,14,Fin Lancashire, on 25 June at 8.50am.
OL,16,FAn eight-year-old girl, who was also
OL,17,Fin the car alongside her remains in a
OL,18,Fcritical but stable condition in
OL,19,Fhospital, British Transport Police
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
