PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782818297
OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,FA criminal investigation has now been
OL,7,Flaunched into the incident, asking
OL,8,Fpeople "not to speculate" on the
OL,9,Fcircumstances.
OL,11,FIn a tribute to the mum, Kerry's
OL,12,Ffamily said: "Kerry was a loving
OL,13,Fdaughter, sister, partner and devoted
OL,14,Fmum who meant everything to us.
OL,16,F"She had the biggest heart, always put
OL,17,Fother people before herself and
OL,18,Fbrought so much love, laughter and
OL,19,Fkindness into the lives of everyone
OL,20,Fwho knew her.
OL,26,@tD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782818297
OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,F"The loss of Kerry has left a hole in
OL,7,Four family that can never be filled.
OL,8,FWe are heartbroken and are trying to
OL,9,Fcome to terms with what has happened."
OL,11,FKerry worked as a "dedicated" social
OL,12,Fworker at Lancashire County Council,
OL,13,Fwho "cared deeply about the children
OL,14,Fshe supported", its head has said.
OL,26,@qD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
