FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782818297
OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,FJacqui Old, Executive Director of
OL,7,FEducation and Children's Services,
OL,8,FLancashire County Council said: "Kerry
OL,9,Fwas a highly respected and dedicated
OL,10,Fsocial worker who cared deeply about
OL,11,Fthe children and families she
OL,12,Fsupported.
OL,14,F"She brought compassion,
OL,15,Fprofessionalism and a strong sense of
OL,16,Fcommitment to her work, and made a
OL,17,Freal difference to people's lives.
OL,26,@pD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782818297
OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,F"She was a valued member of the team
OL,7,Fand will be greatly missed by her
OL,8,Fcolleagues and by all those who knew
OL,9,Fher."
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,Fcrossing after the 07.51 Northern
OL,13,FTrain service from Colne to Preston.
OL,15,FNo passengers were injured during the
OL,16,Fincident and the Rail Accident
OL,17,FInvestigation Branch is also involved
OL,18,Fin the investigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
