PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1782818297
OL,3,CTributes to mum with 'the biggest
OL,4,Cheart' who died on level crossing
OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Paul Attwell said:
OL,8,F"This was a shocking and tragic
OL,9,Fincident, and our specialist officers
OL,10,Fwill continue to support Kerry's
OL,11,Ffamily and friends throughout this
OL,12,Fordeal.
OL,14,F"Following our initial enquiries a
OL,15,Fcriminal investigation into the
OL,16,Fincident has now been launched, and I
OL,17,Fwould ask the public not to speculate
OL,18,Fon the incident, as further updates
OL,19,Fwill be provided in due course."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
